People commenting on the speed of the app need to realise that the app can only display the data from your phone's sensors as fast as your phone sends them. If it's slow, your sensors are slow. You need a better phone, not a better app.  Ditto for accuracy. If your sensors aren't accurate this app *cannot* be accurate - and neither can any other app that depends on those sensors.
